                            <ul>
                                <li>The code attribute will contain a value from the list of codes in the DataQualityInvestigationReason vocabulary;     </li>
                            </ul>
                            <ul>
                                <li>The codeSystem attribute will contain the OID referenced in the DataQualityInvestigationReason vocabulary</li>
                            </ul>
